OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777655154
OL,3,CPrison tutor jailed for 'intimate
OL,4,Crelationship' with inmate
OL,6,FA prison tutor has been jailed after
OL,7,Fadmitting having an intimate
OL,8,Frelationship with an inmate, which was
OL,9,Fdescribed as a "foolish infatuation"
OL,10,Fby a judge.
OL,12,FKelly Duffey, 36, of Amesbury,
OL,13,FWiltshire, was sentenced to 12 months
OL,14,Fin prison at Winchester Crown Court on
OL,15,FFriday over two charges of misconduct
OL,16,Fin a public office in connection with
OL,17,Fthe affair with Ashley Goodridge at
OL,18,FHMP Erlestoke.
OL,26,@qD@POUqD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
