OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777655154
OL,3,CPrison tutor jailed for 'intimate
OL,4,Crelationship' with inmate
OL,6,FThe 38-year-old prisoner, who is
OL,7,Fserving a lengthy IPP sentence for
OL,8,Fcannabis production, was also handed a
OL,9,F12-month prison sentence to run
OL,10,Fconcurrently after pleading guilty to
OL,11,Fhaving a phone and using it to send a
OL,12,Fphoto from the category C men's prison.
OL,14,FThe court heard Duffey moved from full-
OL,15,Ftime teaching work to assist at the
OL,16,FWiltshire jail's education department
OL,17,Fin May 2024, and had an intimate
OL,18,Frelationship with Goodridge between
OL,19,FJuly and September of that year.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777655154
OL,3,CPrison tutor jailed for 'intimate
OL,4,Crelationship' with inmate
OL,6,FShe also knew of another member of
OL,7,Fstaff, a librarian, working at the
OL,8,Fprison who had an intimate
OL,9,Frelationship with another prisoner.
OL,11,FMessages like "I love you" and photos
OL,12,Fwere exchanged between the pair, the
OL,13,Fcourt heard.
OL,15,FDuffey also messaged a friend on
OL,16,FAugust 20 reading: "Definitely done
OL,17,Fsomething this morning I shouldn't
OL,18,Fhave."
OL,26,@sD@OOUsD@ZO]xD@TOUzD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
