OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777655154
OL,3,CPrison tutor jailed for 'intimate
OL,4,Crelationship' with inmate
OL,6,FShe also told her friend of speaking
OL,7,Fto the librarian of her affair who
OL,8,Ftold her where they go and that they
OL,9,Fhad nearly been caught before, adding:
OL,10,F"Talked about an hour about it
OL,11,Fgiggling like school girls lol."
OL,13,FAddressing the defendant, Judge
OL,14,FChristopher Parker KC said as a woman
OL,15,Fin your mid 30s you appeared to be
OL,16,F"overwhelmed by a foolish infatuation".
OL,26,@rD@AOUsD@`O]xD@AOUxD@fO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
