PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777655154
OL,3,CPrison tutor jailed for 'intimate
OL,4,Crelationship' with inmate
OL,6,F"In your correspondence with your
OL,7,Ffriend outside prison it is plain you
OL,8,Fknew the risks, you knew of the
OL,9,Fdangers, you knew what you were doing
OL,10,Fwas wrong," the judge said.
OL,12,F"As far as harm is concerned you
OL,13,Fexposed yourself to the risk of
OL,14,Fblackmail, you exposed yourself to the
OL,15,Frisk of being coerced into committing
OL,16,Fsecurity breaches, or smuggling
OL,17,Fequipment into prison.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777655154
OL,3,CPrison tutor jailed for 'intimate
OL,4,Crelationship' with inmate
OL,6,F"To your credit you did not breach
OL,7,Fsecurity and you did not smuggle any
OL,8,Farticles into prison even though you
OL,9,Fwere invited to do so."
OL,11,FThe judge added that Duffey's
OL,12,Fattachment to Goodridge "in hindsight
OL,13,Fappears to be rather one-sided", but
OL,14,F"was heartfelt and strongly binding as
OL,15,Ffar as you were concerned".
OL,17,FThe court also heard on Duffey's
OL,18,Fbehalf that she expressed regret and
OL,19,Fis very candid about mistakes she has
OL,20,Fmade.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@WO]tD@YOUuD@_O]vD@AOUwD@ZO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
