CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777655154
OL,3,CPrison tutor jailed for 'intimate
OL,4,Crelationship' with inmate
OL,6,FFor Goodridge, it was heard he has
OL,7,Fused his time in custody well,
OL,8,Ftraining as a roofer, qualified in
OL,9,Ftraffic management and will be in a
OL,10,Fposition to work gainfully when
OL,11,Freleased from prison, where he has
OL,12,Fserved "much longer than ever
OL,13,Fenvisaged for a relatively unserious
OL,14,Foffence", his barrister said.
OL,16,FReacting to the sentencing, South West
OL,17,FRegional Organised Crime Unit (SWROCU)
OL,18,Fcounter corruption investigator Pc
OL,19,FMark Paterson said: "The conduct
OL,20,Fdisplayed by Kelly Duffey will not be
OL,21,Ftolerated within a prison estate.
OL,26,@tD@HOUvD@HO]{D@UOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
