OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777655154
OL,3,CPrison tutor jailed for 'intimate
OL,4,Crelationship' with inmate
OL,6,F"She may not have been a prison
OL,7,Fofficer or directly employed by HMPPS,
OL,8,Fbut she was in a position of trust as
OL,9,Fan education tutor, a key role in
OL,10,Fprisoner rehabilitation.
OL,12,F"She misconducted herself and
OL,13,Fneglected her duty over an extended
OL,14,Fperiod of time, which compromised the
OL,15,Fsafety of other staff and inmates.
OL,17,F"The SWROCU Counter Corruption Unit
OL,18,Fwill continue to work alongside HMPPS
OL,19,Fand the CPS to bring to justice anyone
OL,20,Fworking within the prison estate who
OL,21,Fcommits criminal acts."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU}D@WO]
